~ rockSecret
Rocko: So, even though [i]I[/i] can't move, i can make everything else move around me!
do States.rock_eye_animation()
do States.set_timer(3.5)
Rocko: woooooo
- Intriguing.
- Fascinating.
- Tell me more.
Rocko: Look, if I make my eyes go far apart, it looks like those two rocks over there are kissing!
do States.rock_eye_animation()
do States.set_timer(3.5)
Rocko: Isn't that cool?
- Indeed
- But your eyes are far apart. Shouldn't things look farther apart?
	Rocko: Perhaps in some realities. But in the projection of my rock-brain, it's like I'm zooming out! Everything is closer, in the projection of my perception.
Rocko: Isn't that the neatest
- I admit, it's pretty cool.
- That's pretty weird.
- You've got a lot of free time, Rocko.
Rocko: Yeah I know. I'm [i]awesome[/i].
Rocko: I'm so happy to be your friend. I hope you come back and chill!
=> END


~ rockjustfriends
Plato: Sometimes the answer is not to jump in. Take your time.
Plata : By the by, we're just friends. 
Plato: [i]Forever[/i]
Plata: Almost, but never quite close enough. We yearn.
